text: George Powell (12 April 1918 - 11 April 1994) was an Australian cricketer. He played four first-class matches for New South Wales between 1941/42 and 1948/49. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1918 births Category:1994 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
